consensus.methodology:
This consensus report synthesizes findings from three specialized agents:
1. Econometric Agent (35% weight): Focuses on causality, cointegration, and structural relationships
2. Machine Learning Agent (35% weight): Identifies non-linear patterns and feature importance
3. Statistical Agent (30% weight): Performs classical correlation and distribution analysis

Each agent independently analyzes relationships, then findings are aggregated using weighted voting. Agreement levels indicate consistency across methodologies, with unanimous agreement providing highest confidence.
